      "content": "That's a good start for the overview. To really win the debate, I need more specific \"intellectual\" depth. Can you expand on the idea of \"societal dilution\"? I want to argue that integration actually causes social friction and erodes the unique character of ethnic neighborhoods. How would a proponent at the time have argued that keeping groups separate is actually more \"humane\" or \"stable\" than forced integration? Give me some more concrete points on that.",
